title: non-cancerous surrounding tissue-1
treatment_protocol_ch1: Samples from colorectal cancer patients were processed with routine methods for snap frozen and stored in liquid nitrogen until use.
extract_protocol_ch1: Trizol (Thermo Fisher Scientific) extraction of total RNA was performed according to the manufacturer's instructions.
label_protocol_ch1: Biotinylated cRNA were prepared according to the standard Affymetrix protocol from 12 ug total RNA (Expression Analysis Technical Manual, 2001, Affymetrix).
hyb_protocol: Following fragmentation(94 °C for 35 min), 10 ug of cRNA were hybridized for 16 hr at 45℃(60 rpm) on PrimeView™ Human Gene Expression Array. GeneChips were washed and stained in the Affymetrix Fluidics Station 450.
scan_protocol: GeneChips were scanned using the GeneChip® Scanner 3000
description: Gene expression data from non-cancerous colorectal tissue
data_processing: The data were analyzed with RMA using Affymetrix default analysis settings and global scaling as normalization method.
contact_institute: Fujian University of Traditional Chinese Medicine
